Business Brief -- Stolt Tankers  Terminals:
   Purchase of a Comex Unit
   Is Planned at $44.6 Million
The agreement, expected to be completed by May, calls for
Stolt to pay $30 million in cash and 750,000 of its shares,
valued at a total $14.6 million at yesterday's closing price
of $19.25 a share in national over-the-counter trading.